[SN]TITLE[SN]
The 'world's longest' garage sale on US Highway 127

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
An annual weekend garage sale along Highway 127, from Michigan to Alabama, in the US has begun.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Media playback is unsupported on your device
8 August 2015 Last updated at 13:53 BST
People along the route turn their front gardens, which they call yards, into shops and sell unwanted household items and toys, along with food and drink.
The sale is now in its 28th year and around 5,000 vendors are expected to take part.
